name: Backrooms: Liminal Hell
description:
This game isn't out yet and I made this page to share current game build with my testers, but I made it public because I am sure it won't get popular until I finally finish it so anyone can also check it at current stage and leave feedback if they want to.

The game contains placeholder models, sounds and animations - these aren't final.
Main gameplay is 90% done, it's playable, but still requires changing some gameplay variables in the final verison.

You can die here, and the game is challenging.

Your only goal: escape the level. Good luck! I hope you enjoy the gameplay!
